post.desc:
Man, I can almost smell what a toxic hellscape Gensokyo Twitter will be like.

I was about to come up with a name for the Twitter equivalent with a Gensokyo flair, and then I realized. Twitter definitely exists in Gensokyo, because as we all know, it has already... [***passed into fantasy.***](https://twitter.com/akarinomiya_a/status/1683480673594621953)
